data.description: Nestled along the tree-lined streets of Morningside Estates, this spacious home offers a welcoming atmosphere and ample living space. With a three-car garage and a picturesque backyard, it's perfect for relaxation and entertaining. Just minutes from I68, it's ideal for commuters and conveniently located near Morgantown's downtown and Cheat Lake areas.  Inside, a grand two-story foyer welcomes you, leading to a modern great room that flows seamlessly to the back patio. The large kitchen features new appliances, a reverse osmosis drinking water filtration system, a cozy breakfast nook, and countertop seating. A formal dining room and dedicated office space add versatility.  Upstairs, four generously sized bedrooms offer privacy, with bedroom-level laundry for added convenience.  The lower level of the home features an egress window and an additional full bath, making it an ideal space for a recreational room or private living quarters.  A large unfinished storage room provides ample space for organizing belongings or future customization.  With its charming location and thoughtful amenities, this home in Morningside Estates offers comfort, convenience, and style.
